org.locationtech.geowave.analytic.mapreduce.dbscan

Class DBScanClusterList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.analytic.mapreduce.dbscan.DBScanClusterList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<Map.Entry<ByteArray,ClusterItem>>, Cluster, NeighborList<ClusterItem>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClusterUnionList, SingleItemClusterList

    public abstract class DBScanClusterList
extends Object
implements Cluster
    Represents a cluster. Maintains links to other clusters through shared components Maintains counts contributed by components of this cluster. Supports merging with other clusters, incrementing the count by only those components different from the other cluster.

    Intended to run in a single thread. Not Thread Safe.
